<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3153383" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="U" oldref="1"><link href="text/shared/01/05070600.xhp" name="Align Bottom">Align Bottom</link></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3154613" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="2"><ahelp hid=".">Vertically aligns the bottom edges of the selected objects. If only one object is selected in Draw or Impress, the bottom edge of the object is aligned to the lower page margin.</ahelp></paragraph>
</section>
<section id="howtoget">
<embed href="text/shared/00/00040501.xhp#unten"/>
</section>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3151330" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="4">Objects are aligned to the bottom edge of the bottom most object in the selection. <embedvar href="text/shared/01/05070100.xhp#mehrfachselektion"/>
</paragraph>
